title: Ken Paxton Is Re-elected Texas Attorney General
description: A perennial Republican political survivor and a Trump loyalist, he won a third term, defeating a progressive civil rights lawyer.
dc:creator: J. David Goodman

media:content.media:credit: Cooper Neill for The New York Times
media:content.media:description: Ken Paxton won a third term as attorney general of Texas, overcoming accusations of corruption and securities fraud.
